    <title>Rails 初學筆記 (三) - Ruby 基礎說明</title>
    <link href="https://anxgang.github.io/post/series/S02_rails/C01_rails_starter/series-rails-starter-03.html"/>
    <id>https://anxgang.github.io/post/series/S02_rails/C01_rails_starter/series-rails-starter-03.html</id>
    <published>2020-03-24T23:30:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-25T03:06:52.956Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/post/series/S02_rails/C01_rails_starter/rails_starter.jpg" alt></p><h2 id="IRB-Interactive-Ruby"><a href="#IRB-Interactive-Ruby" class="headerlink" title="IRB(Interactive Ruby)"></a>IRB(Interactive Ruby)</h2><p>IRB 是一個互動的 Ruby 環境，可以讓我們練習和語法</p><p>輸入 irb 就會進入互動模式</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">irb</span><br><span class="line">2.6.3 :001 &gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如要跳出可以按下鍵盤的 <code>ctrl + d</code></p><p>以下範例都可以使用 irb 練習</p><h2 id="輸出"><a href="#輸出" class="headerlink" title="輸出"></a>輸出</h2><h4 id="puts"><a href="#puts" class="headerlink" title="puts"></a>puts</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">puts <span class="string">'hello'</span> <span class="comment"># =&gt; hello</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="註解"><a href="#註解" class="headerlink" title="註解"></a>註解</h2><h4 id="單行註解"><a href="#單行註解" class="headerlink" title="單行註解"></a>單行註解</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># xxx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="多行註解"><a href="#多行註解" class="headerlink" title="多行註解"></a>多行註解</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">=begin</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  xxx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  xxx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">=end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="資料型態"><a href="#資料型態" class="headerlink" title="資料型態"></a>資料型態</h2><h4 id="整數-Integer"><a href="#整數-Integer" class="headerlink" title="整數 Integer"></a>整數 Integer</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">123</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>+<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>/<span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="浮點數-Float"><a href="#浮點數-Float" class="headerlink" title="浮點數 Float"></a>浮點數 Float</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.2</span>+<span class="number">3.6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字串-String"><a href="#字串-String" class="headerlink" title="字串 String"></a>字串 String</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span> <span class="comment"># 需用『單引號』或『雙引號』包起來</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"123"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="常數-Constant"><a href="#常數-Constant" class="headerlink" title="常數 Constant"></a>常數 Constant</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">HELLO = <span class="string">'123'</span> <span class="comment">#全大寫</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="空值-nil"><a href="#空值-nil" class="headerlink" title="空值 nil"></a>空值 nil</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="literal">nil</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="符號-Symbols"><a href="#符號-Symbols" class="headerlink" title="符號 Symbols"></a>符號 Symbols</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">:hello</span> = <span class="string">'123'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="陣列-Array"><a href="#陣列-Array" class="headerlink" title="陣列 Array"></a>陣列 Array</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">'a'</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="雜湊-Hash"><a href="#雜湊-Hash" class="headerlink" title="雜湊 Hash"></a>雜湊 Hash</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;<span class="symbol">:a</span> =&gt; <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="symbol">:b</span> =&gt; <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="symbol">:c</span> =&gt; <span class="number">3</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;<span class="string">'a'</span> =&gt; <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span> =&gt; <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span> =&gt; <span class="number">3</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;<span class="symbol">a:</span> <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="symbol">b:</span> <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="symbol">c:</span> <span class="number">3</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Array-和-Hash-混合使用"><a href="#Array-和-Hash-混合使用" class="headerlink" title="Array 和 Hash 混合使用"></a>Array 和 Hash 混合使用</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;<span class="symbol">:a</span> =&gt; <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="symbol">:b</span> =&gt; <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="symbol">:c</span> =&gt; <span class="number">3</span>&#125;, </span><br><span class="line">  &#123;<span class="symbol">:a</span> =&gt; <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="symbol">:b</span> =&gt; <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="symbol">:c</span> =&gt; <span class="number">6</span>&#125;, </span><br><span class="line">  &#123;<span class="symbol">:a</span> =&gt; <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="symbol">:b</span> =&gt; <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="symbol">:c</span> =&gt; <span class="number">9</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;<span class="symbol">a:</span> <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="symbol">b:</span> <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="symbol">c:</span> <span class="number">3</span>&#125;, </span><br><span class="line">  &#123;<span class="symbol">a:</span> <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="symbol">b:</span> <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="symbol">c:</span> <span class="number">6</span>&#125;, </span><br><span class="line">  &#123;<span class="symbol">a:</span> <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="symbol">b:</span> <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="symbol">c:</span> <span class="number">9</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="字串處理"><a href="#字串處理" class="headerlink" title="字串處理"></a>字串處理</h2><h4 id="相加"><a href="#相加" class="headerlink" title="相加"></a>相加</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span> + <span class="string">'world'</span> <span class="comment">#=&gt; "helloworld"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="取位"><a href="#取位" class="headerlink" title="取位"></a>取位</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>[<span class="number">0</span>] <span class="comment"># =&gt; "h"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="comment"># =&gt; "e"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>[<span class="number">0</span>..<span class="number">3</span>] <span class="comment"># =&gt; "hell"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>[<span class="number">0</span>...<span class="number">3</span>] <span class="comment"># =&gt; "hel"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>[<span class="number">0</span>..-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="comment"># =&gt; "hello"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="取代-gsub"><a href="#取代-gsub" class="headerlink" title="取代 gsub"></a>取代 gsub</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello world'</span>.gsub(<span class="string">'o'</span>,<span class="string">'a'</span>) <span class="comment"># =&gt; "hella warld"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello world'</span>.gsub(<span class="string">'world'</span>,<span class="string">'ruby'</span>) <span class="comment"># =&gt; "hello ruby"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="分組-split"><a href="#分組-split" class="headerlink" title="分組 split"></a>分組 split</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>.split <span class="comment"># =&gt; ["hello"]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello'</span>.split(<span class="string">''</span>) <span class="comment"># =&gt; ["h", "e", "l", "l", "o"]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello, world'</span>.split(<span class="string">''</span>) <span class="comment"># =&gt; ["h", "e", "l", "l", "o", ",", " ", "w", "o", "r", "l", "d"]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello, world'</span>.split() <span class="comment"># =&gt; ["hello,", "world"]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'hello world'</span>.split(<span class="string">' '</span>) <span class="comment"># =&gt; ["hello", "world"]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="變數"><a href="#變數" class="headerlink" title="變數"></a>變數</h2><h4 id="宣告"><a href="#宣告" class="headerlink" title="宣告"></a>宣告</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hello = <span class="string">'hello'</span></span><br><span class="line">@hello = <span class="string">'world'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字串內使用變數"><a href="#字串內使用變數" class="headerlink" title="字串內使用變數"></a>字串內使用變數</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">puts <span class="string">"<span class="subst">#&#123;hello&#125;</span> world"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="流程"><a href="#流程" class="headerlink" title="流程"></a>流程</h2><h4 id="if"><a href="#if" class="headerlink" title="if"></a>if</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> hello==<span class="string">'world'</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'NO'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">elsif</span> hello==<span class="string">'hello'</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'YES'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'NA'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="case"><a href="#case" class="headerlink" title="case"></a>case</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> hello</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">when</span> <span class="string">'hello'</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'YES'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">when</span> <span class="string">'world'</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'NO'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'NA'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="each"><a href="#each" class="headerlink" title="each"></a>each</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">5</span>.times.each <span class="keyword">do</span> <span class="params">|num|</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts num</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">'hello'</span>,<span class="string">'world'</span>].each <span class="keyword">do</span> <span class="params">|word|</span></span><br><span class="line">  puts word</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="方法"><a href="#方法" class="headerlink" title="方法"></a>方法</h2><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">hello</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  puts <span class="string">'world'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="類別"><a href="#類別" class="headerlink" title="類別"></a>類別</h2><h4 id="class"><a href="#class" class="headerlink" title="class"></a>class</h4><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 父類別</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Human</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 類別方法 class method</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">self</span>.<span class="title">hello</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    puts <span class="string">"All <span class="subst">#&#123;<span class="keyword">self</span>.name&#125;</span> hello"</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 實例方法 instance method</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">hello</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    puts <span class="string">"Single <span class="subst">#&#123;<span class="keyword">self</span><span class="class">.<span class="keyword">class</span>.<span class="title">name</span>&#125; <span class="title">hello</span>"</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst">  <span class="keyword">end</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"><span class="keyword">end</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"><span class="comment"># 子類別</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Man</span> &lt; Human</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"><span class="keyword">end</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Women</span> &lt; Human</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="subst"><span class="keyword">end</span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 父類別 直接呼叫 類別方法</span></span><br><span class="line">Human.hello</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 父類別 建立實例 並 由實例呼叫實例方法</span></span><br><span class="line">human = Human.new</span><br><span class="line">human.hello</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 子類別 直接呼叫 父類別方法 (類別方法繼承)</span></span><br><span class="line">Man.hello</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 子類別 建立實例 並 由實例呼叫父類別實例方法 (實例方法繼承)</span></span><br><span class="line">man = Man.new</span><br><span class="line">man.hello</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>參考</p><ol><li><a href="https://ihower.tw/rails/ruby.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ihower.tw/rails/ruby.html</a></li><li><a href="https://railsbook.tw/chapters/05-ruby-basic-1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://railsbook.tw/chapters/05-ruby-basic-1.html</a></li><li><a href="https://railsbook.tw/chapters/06-ruby-basic-2.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://railsbook.tw/chapters/06-ruby-basic-2.html</a></li><li><a href="https://railsbook.tw/chapters/07-ruby-basic-3.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://railsbook.tw/chapters/07-ruby-basic-3.html</a></li><li><a href="https://railsbook.tw/chapters/08-ruby-basic-4.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://railsbook.tw/chapters/08-ruby-basic-4.html</a></li></ol></blockquote>]]></content>
    
